{
  "text": "The cnidome of the early life stages of C. barnesi was found to be identical to the cnidome of the adults. This deviates from other cubozoan species which change their cnidome between polyp and medusa stages [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
